Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上泡澡最舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符姐姐 请让我帮您搓背
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二话 兵者诡道也
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮我传话给那个孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早饭前的泡澡要适可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要带她回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说一定要带她回家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我可从来没有听过你还有个妹妹...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你这个笨女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服又被你给弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...这是有那个...很深的原因的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙权仲谋 今年16岁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也重新自我介绍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 孙策伯符 16岁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周瑜公瑾 同样是16岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照 仲谋小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲谋...小姐...吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说周瑜大人和伯符姐姐 是像姐弟一样被抚养大的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 可不可以像称呼伯符姐姐那样来叫我仲谋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很过分的请求吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没...没有那回事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教...仲谋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是要请多多指教呢 公瑾哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 我就是你的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吴荣17岁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲谋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符 早饭做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符 要细嚼慢咽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 再来一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子不听别人说话呢 这个笨女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得没那个心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是我不小心 真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 这不是你的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用啊 公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裸体你不是早就看惯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾哥哥 刚才你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 我们从小开始每天都在一起玩赤膊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有每...每天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更正过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 是差不多每天都...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:04:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 只有在玩的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲谋的南阳入学手续已经办好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 阿姨...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子真的是伯符的妹妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STOP 太在意细节问题可是不会受女生欢迎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾 久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 好好去学习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行啊 走路东张西望的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个 在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 伯符姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸好红啊 还流汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:05:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子可能发烧了...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是第一次来这里上学 有点不安而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有人欺负你 我会把他打飞的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打...打飞？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策的妹妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初...初次见面 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此 多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你喜欢甜食吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小乐啊 超喜欢吃甜食的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我也很喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向你推荐车站对面巧克力店的 抹茶奶油珍珠豆沙冰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和孙策完全不像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:06:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 不像姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 孙策伯符的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然比不上姐姐的巨乳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮廓也很有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袁胤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像往常一样 把她吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 汗味太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失...失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你们也舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你们乖乖地听话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要以为你可以一直都坐在当家的宝座上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:07:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲谋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只小猫怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 其实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.38,0:08:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么怎么办 你不是都已经捡回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是 你能放着不管吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它还这么小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 确实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家里养吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符根本就不会照顾猫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连自己的房间都收拾不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀...说到痛处了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算了 我在学校里养
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我问你 你能把养育的责任负责到底吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:08:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可...可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:08:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能保证吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能 我和你约定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是伯符那个家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是厉害 还有那样的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家才会追随她作为当家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于突然出现的我 她完全没有抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱怨什么的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论什么时候 你都可以留在那个家里的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天每天都喝牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定厌倦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:10:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到猫 当然是要吃鱼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗 我们的笨蛋当家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近好像在体育馆后面养了只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是因为跟人类无法沟通 所以只能和猫聊天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 那可不是一般的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算不上是人类的笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还真是给四天王添麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都要面对那样的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正四天王也只是把她当作挡箭牌利用罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个笨蛋没有作为当家的资格这点是肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从下午课开始就不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是什么稀奇的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在开始要去打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工？啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙可不可以代替她一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说...说过的 我不适合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的制服是很漂亮的女仆装
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得吕蒙一定会喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 周瑜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 孙权
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您走好 吕蒙大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾哥哥 请恕我多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:11:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很诱人的鱼饵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在沮丧什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小...小蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做和你性格不相符的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我笑得都停不下来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实小蒙也是把我当成一个笨蛋当家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这里还有在背地里说闲话的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是闲话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确不全是闲话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个笨蛋这点是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为君主是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:13:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么问我...哎呀 我是个笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当家的背后有数百的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 背负了数百人的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数百人的梦想...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 抱着这些梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有一个人也要保护所有的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是当家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做这种费力不讨好的事的人 没有几个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策 除了像你这样的笨蛋以外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又叫我笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干...干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是很明白 不过恢复精神了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是要有朋友才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友...吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策 周瑜在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:14:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 小蒙 明天见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐就吗 有点事情想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 完全迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符 抱歉 我太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲谋她...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.97,0:14:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 伯符 这是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是陷阱也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是当家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...这里是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干...干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张照片会传到我们老大创立的网站上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的老大？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是袁胤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袁胤是前当家袁术的直属斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传闻袁术倒台后 他就一直想成为新当家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 穿制服的拍这些应该够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面就是里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面的事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袁胤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不记得我有拜托过你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你就是袁胤先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用叫得这么见外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你可以叫我主人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐惧中的女生的汗的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救...救我 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一群没情趣的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在这个时候登场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不解风情也要有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要找的人是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你肯听我的话为止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你下一道命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:16:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下令由我袁胤接任现当家孙策伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而成为新一代的当家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我说不呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹怎么样都无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再敢碰她一根手指的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会放过你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙子曰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟起者 伏也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟群飞起 预示着有伏兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了如此聪明的我怎么可能一个人来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的是那么认为的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就真的是笨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和你这种卑鄙小人不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:18:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟...竟然说大话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你打倒我之后 再重新听你的废话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧 小弟们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袁...袁胤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐...乐就
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看南阳四天王间的牵绊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经没有胜算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧 袁胤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 我投降
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我要你们后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有听从我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去后悔一辈子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:18:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策 放手去干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙 多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...不...那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢对我可爱的妹妹下手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要打飞你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 公瑾哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会呢 不过还好平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 谢谢你 伯符姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始就很在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我买的鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾 帮帮我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑滑的拿不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 为什么要买干鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问吗 给小猫的...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 今天忘记喂它吃午饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喂过它牛奶了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 谢谢你 公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符姐姐 我有事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从明天开始 我也可以去喂小猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 非常欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 仲谋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是第一次叫我仲谋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 现在去车站对面的那家巧克力店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去吃那个抹茶奶油珍珠豆沙冰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 偶尔也...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？怎么了 小蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:20:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙又...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.38,0:21:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追丢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布...奉先
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.17,0:21:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么...你会...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.21,0:23:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 孙策
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.54,0:23:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在校舍后面养的那只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可...可以也让我抱抱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.64,0:23:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要是让小乐抱的话 小猫就碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.47,0:23:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么说 一次就好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.54,0:23:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 让我抱抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.47,0:23:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐就大人 请您冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.73,0:23:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为斗士 不论何时都必须保持冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我想抱 现在就让我抱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三话 死者不可复生
